Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.46,0:00:20.35,Alt,,0,0,0,,﻿Memorial Corner\NAina Sakurai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.81,0:00:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Wow, this girl ﻿died.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.52,0:00:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿A cute thing ﻿like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.82,0:00:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Hey, she was ﻿the same age as us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.65,0:00:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Poor thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.99,0:00:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿That's so lame, ﻿I hate those Dorssians...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.03,0:00:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Rest in peace, ﻿Aina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.80,0:00:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.47,0:00:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.09,0:00:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Just you ﻿watch, Nobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Next time, I'm gonna avenge you ﻿in that robot for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.60,0:01:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'll avenge you, ﻿you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.65,0:01:04.77,Alt,,0,0,0,,﻿REST IN PEACE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.27,0:01:13.74,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\pos(974,74)\fs36}Tokishima Haruto
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.27,0:01:13.74,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\pos(978,580)\fs36}L-elf Karlstein
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.25,0:01:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I've worked out ﻿everyone's assignments.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.08,0:01:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Six systems are integrated at Command:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.71,0:01:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Navigation, ﻿Gunnery, Communications, Radar, Engineering, Shields.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.05,0:01:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Are you sure you want to let me ﻿work up the battle station assignments?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.93,0:01:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm asking you to do it because I think ﻿that's the best way to minimize loss of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.22,0:01:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Aina Sakurai, ﻿huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.60,0:01:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I've decided to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.52,0:01:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That you also have something precious to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.08,0:02:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It looks like the intervals between ﻿attacks are growing shorter...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.97,0:02:15.01,Alt,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.30,0:03:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Training Journal. ﻿Rion Nanami.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Module 77 is en route to the Moon ﻿which is neutral territory.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.11,0:04:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿The students have begun military drills ﻿in order to prepare for battle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.95,0:04:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿The person who drew up the drill regimen was ﻿none other than L-elf, our country's first refugee.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.29,0:04:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿I think the reason that the students have been ﻿so surprisingly quick to accept his instructions{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.08,0:04:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿is that they don't want to see ﻿anyone else die.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.59,0:04:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿I myself am teaching ﻿first-aid procedures.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.47,0:04:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Though I hate the thought of ﻿any of my students being hurt...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿I take some comfort in the fact that lessons are ﻿still being conducted in the classrooms.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Inuzuka, quit looking at those ﻿stock prices or whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.44,0:04:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Intruder detected in the Pit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿I repeat, intruder detected in the Pit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.49,0:04:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿An enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.83,0:04:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Our "intruder" was ﻿Yamada, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿This is the fifth time. ﻿When is he gonna learn?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.21,0:05:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I get it. ﻿He wants to use this to—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿He wants to use it to get revenge ﻿with his own two hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.01,0:05:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.01,0:05:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanting to avenge ﻿a friend's death is pathetic?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.39,0:05:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿These machines have ﻿a registration system.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.27,0:05:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Once one pilot uses it, it can't be ﻿changed over to another.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.48,0:05:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿If I gave in to emotion and let someone pilot it, ﻿and it turned out that he had no talent for it, what then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Nothing is a bigger nuisance than ﻿the hopes of people who have no talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.95,0:05:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Will avenging someone's death ﻿bring them back to life?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.41,0:05:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Instead of that, you should think about ﻿how to prevent future losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿War is something that should be conducted ﻿calmly and efficiently, like a machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.05,0:05:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Like a ﻿machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿47 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.56,0:06:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿46 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿48 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.32,0:06:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿44 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Is he okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:18.54,Alt,,0,0,0,,﻿Is he okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Haru—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿What're you ﻿doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I was worried about him. ﻿What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.51,0:06:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm worried, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.09,0:06:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I wonder if ﻿they were going out...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.30,0:06:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Him and ﻿Aina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.68,0:06:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿They were joined ﻿at the hip.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿He was always heading out ﻿to visit some girl from another school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.81,0:06:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.73,0:06:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Haruto. ﻿Say something to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿This is too big ﻿to carry alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Why not you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.70,0:06:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This has to be done ﻿guy to guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Yamada's ﻿at it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.70,0:06:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿No. Yamada's supposed to be ﻿in solitary confinement.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿A Dorssian fleet is ﻿closing in on us from behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.54,0:07:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿The barrier ﻿system?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Already ﻿on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.21,0:07:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿We won't let them ﻿hit us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm widening ﻿mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿What are ﻿those?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.56,0:07:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿The barrier system ﻿seems to be working.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.31,0:07:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Way to go! You guys are ﻿great at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿I can't believe he retrofitted the EM debris shield ﻿into a barrier system...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.36,0:07:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿How long had he been ﻿planning it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Calmly. ﻿Like a machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.18,0:07:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Calmly. ﻿Like a machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.48,0:08:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿A systematic ﻿defense strategy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿L-elf is ﻿in command?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.42,0:08:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It's the ﻿Valvraves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Fall back slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Draw them both away from Module 77.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿They're ﻿running?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿My show's just ﻿getting started!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.35,0:08:44.10,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}DORSSIA MILITARY\N﻿#6 FLEET{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Exactly ﻿as planned, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.98,0:08:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿The Valvraves are moving away ﻿to aft in pursuit of Captain Cain's fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.61,0:08:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿They're only students, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.75,0:08:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe ﻿they fell for such an obvious diversion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.13,0:09:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Wow, the Valvraves ﻿are so powerful...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.68,0:09:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿They're our ﻿guardian angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Still, aren't they too powerful?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,JIOR didn't have ﻿any weapon manufacturers, so how—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.98,0:09:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Ration time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.56,0:09:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Those look ﻿tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.81,0:09:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.77,0:09:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm starved!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.61,0:09:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Emergency rations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.42,0:09:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You told me ﻿to make some, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.90,0:09:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿What did you do ﻿with the recipe I gave you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.28,0:09:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It's better if they ﻿taste good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.12,0:09:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿These are a JIOR specialty, ﻿jellied bean paste called "Youkan."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.62,0:09:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿What counts is nutrition. ﻿Flavor doesn't—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.87,0:09:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.12,0:09:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿See? Nice and ﻿sweet, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.17,0:09:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿We've been ﻿making these forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.47,0:09:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿E-Enemy vessels detected!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.73,0:09:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿But Haruto and ﻿Saki chased—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.06,0:09:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿No, these are coming ﻿from up ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.35,0:09:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It's not the same ﻿fleet as before!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.86,0:10:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿They had another ﻿force out here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.52,0:10:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were they hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.28,0:10:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Then we'll just have to ﻿defend against these, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.70,0:10:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿But there's way more ﻿of them this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.04,0:10:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Quit your ﻿whining!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿We don't need Haruto ﻿to defend ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.85,0:10:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿The Module's ﻿being attacked?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.64,0:10:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿A different fleet moved in ﻿when you left!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.68,0:10:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You're saying ﻿we were lured away?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.14,0:10:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Miss Rukino ﻿let's head back!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.19,0:10:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿If you want to go back, ﻿you'll have to go through us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.49,0:10:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿#3 bulkhead ﻿destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Enemy fleet now has us ﻿completely surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.41,0:10:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿The Valvraves are ﻿pinned down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.62,0:10:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You're some kind of war pro, ﻿aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.29,0:11:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿What the—? ﻿What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.67,0:11:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿A power outage?! ﻿Why now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.06,0:11:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.89,0:11:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Hey, what the hell is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.59,0:11:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Open the door! Open the door, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.32,0:11:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Now's ﻿my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.32,0:11:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿What is it? ﻿What caused it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿The barriers must have put too big a strain ﻿on the generator system.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.37,0:11:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You could have mentioned ﻿that might happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.29,0:11:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Did Haruto and Saki ﻿get taken out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.00,0:11:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿That could ﻿never happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.25,0:11:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Then why has ﻿the power gone out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.33,0:11:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Calm down, ﻿people!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.67,0:11:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Inuzuka-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.38,0:11:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Otamaya! Are you in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.38,0:11:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We need you ﻿to get the generators back—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.63,0:11:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Don't do it, Thunder! ﻿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.03,0:11:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing isn't what you think it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.26,0:11:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.66,0:11:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're nothing but a lapdog ﻿tor that stinking detector!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.14,0:12:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You can't! This is—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.48,0:12:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You said you wanted to ﻿get revenge, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.23,0:12:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I know exactly how you feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.23,0:12:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿But that's just your ego talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.65,0:12:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿For everyone to survive, it should be piloted ﻿by someone with the knack for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.95,0:12:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You guys can wallow in your pity party on the net ﻿if you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.72,0:12:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't want any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.33,0:12:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I have to do something! Personally!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.56,0:12:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never be able to ﻿live with myself if I don't get revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.38,0:12:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It's to keep more people from dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.14,0:12:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It's so we can all be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.38,0:12:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"We"? ﻿Who's "we"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.64,0:12:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Does this "we" ﻿include you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Cause a "we" that don't include ﻿yourself don't mean jack!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.03,0:12:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,When she laughed, ﻿it made me happy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.99,0:13:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿She didn't believe in herself, she was kind, and she could be happy for others.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿She didn't like ﻿shiitake mushrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.63,0:13:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿She didn't like tragedies ﻿but she loved horror movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.26,0:13:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿She looked so tiny when she cried ﻿that it made you want to hold her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.26,0:13:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Made you want to kiss her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Made you want to be with her forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.14,0:13:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿What the hell are you ﻿talking about—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.06,0:13:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I don't want to ﻿do this for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.11,0:13:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I want to ﻿fight for myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.28,0:13:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿There are 17 students ﻿with a pilot aptitude of rank A.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.29,0:13:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Of those, the ones with the mindset to get in ﻿voluntarily are the most suitable to be pilots.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.96,0:13:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.67,0:13:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿This is what ﻿happened to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.77,0:14:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I've made up ﻿my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.05,0:14:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Cain was having trouble ﻿against opponents like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.51,0:14:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿In the end, ﻿he's only a spymaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.72,0:14:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿They aren't spies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The Karlstein Agency is ﻿a training school for agents that—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.76,0:14:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.31,0:14:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Main guns, fire at will! ﻿Blow their whole ceiling away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.40,0:14:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Blitzendegen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.53,0:15:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.24,0:15:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿We're done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.54,0:15:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿What the—?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.42,0:15:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Our main ﻿guns!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.79,0:15:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.60,0:15:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿God's touched ﻿me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.23,0:15:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Isn't that ﻿right, Aina?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.45,0:15:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Form up! ﻿Waffen, position 7!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.72,0:16:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿How do you ﻿like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.14,0:16:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Stupid amateur! ﻿Your back is wide open!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.89,0:16:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.03,0:16:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Take that, ﻿you Dorssian dick!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.87,0:16:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Yamada?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It's "Thunder"'!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.91,0:16:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You... ﻿You hit "Yes"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.41,0:16:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Oh, you mean that thing about ﻿resigning humanity or whatever?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.62,0:16:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Oh, you did it, ﻿too...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.55,0:16:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'll explain later! ﻿For now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Yeah! I'm gonna ﻿avenge Nobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.77,0:17:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It has ﻿eight arms?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.23,0:17:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Ten, counting ﻿its original two!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.15,0:17:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I can ﻿see that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.69,0:17:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Superconducting fluid accelerator ﻿cannon, prepare to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.32,0:17:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿But sir! At this angle, ﻿we'll hit our own forces!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.82,0:17:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿That's ﻿an order!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.33,0:18:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Kyuma Inuzuka. ﻿068 is the enemy's flagship.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.17,0:18:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Crush the head ﻿of the snake, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.16,0:18:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿That's a siege cannon meant for ﻿assaulting fortified positions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.30,0:18:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It's not the most ﻿accurate weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.72,0:18:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿But they're between us ﻿and the target!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.73,0:18:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Tell me, Aina...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.05,0:18:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had told you how I felt, ﻿would you have given me the go-ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.74,0:18:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Would it have put you on the spot?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Or would it have made you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.70,0:18:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Aina!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.57,0:19:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.70,0:19:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿The accelerator cannon ﻿was deflected?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.57,0:19:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Sure... ﻿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.32,0:19:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand, Aina!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.75,0:19:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Evasive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.79,0:19:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿There's ﻿no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿No response from ﻿Commodore Manninger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.82,0:19:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿This makes ﻿four people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.15,0:19:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Did they manage to ﻿reproduce them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.74,0:19:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿I knew it, ﻿I didn't mishear him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.36,0:19:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Order all forces to withdraw.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:19:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿This operation is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Thank you, ﻿Inuzuka-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Let me ride with you ﻿next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Hey, I saw you ﻿out there, Inuzuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Weren't you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We can count on you, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Way to go, ﻿Thunder!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.19,0:20:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I was wrong ﻿about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿That's our Thunder!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.14,0:20:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You were awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.65,0:20:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Got anything to say ﻿to me? I piloted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Escaping from solitary counts as a jailbreak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.21,0:20:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You're in for another week.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You— ﻿Not even a freaking "Thank you"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.74,0:20:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.00,0:20:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I never expected to ﻿see you in one of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿What, it's ﻿out of character?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Nope! It's exactly ﻿like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.36,0:20:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,L-elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.43,0:20:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿L-elf! What about ﻿our promise?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿These two decided on their own to get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.24,0:20:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿What could I have done?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.47,0:20:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿That's a load of bull!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.61,0:20:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have been able to tell ﻿that those first enemies were decoys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You give me ﻿too much credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.65,0:21:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.82,0:21:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿This is ﻿for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.61,0:21:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Haruto, from now on, ﻿let us fight alongside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.33,0:21:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I got dumped. Clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Aina told me ﻿not to come join her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.39,0:21:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It isn't working?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.00,0:21:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though ﻿it has an official number designation?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.32,0:21:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Takumi Kibukawa. ﻿ID number JS27-9154277.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.74,0:21:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Master Fellow attached to ﻿the JIOR Army #4 Research Institute.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.25,0:21:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Aside from Rion Nanami, ﻿all the teachers were in the JIOR military.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.63,0:22:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Why was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.59,0:22:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Not just the teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The city residents, ﻿the dock workers, we were all military personnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.97,0:22:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.89,0:22:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Dude, these are ﻿awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.02,0:22:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Okay, let's make these ﻿our local specialty!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.15,0:22:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿When we get to the Moon, we'll get a ton of tourists!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.18,0:22:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿These things will sell like crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.15,0:22:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿We'd better register ﻿a trademark, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.28,0:22:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm saying that Module 77, ﻿even the students...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.20,0:22:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿all of it was created ﻿for the Valvraves.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.43,0:24:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Next time, episode 10, ﻿"Campaign Promise of Love".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.73,0:24:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Valvrave the Liberator...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.50,0:24:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The system that will expose the truth of the world.
